<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="../convention/CCBanquet.gif">
<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="../convention/RalphReed.gif">
The Christian Coalition Banquet had over 1900 people. Here Ralph Reed asks 
delegates to push for a slate of national delegates representing the 80% 
pro-family segment of the San Antonio convention.<BR>
<IMG SRC="../convention/Bush.gif">
After giving a well received speech in the morning, 
Bush welcomes conventioneers to an outdoor luncheon. <BR>
<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="../convention/Division.gif">
<BR><BR><BR><BR>
Delegates call for Division of the House.
<BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR>
<IMG ALIGN=CENTER SRC="../convention/Keyes.gif">
 Alan Keyes greets supporters outside the Alamo.<BR>
